   <conbody>
      <p class="- topic/p ">Compare the components of the shipment with the delivery note.
Report any missing items to the shipping agency and to <xref conref="../Library/Reference_Library_CPT_0000338844.dita#Reference_Library-69E2C789/Reality_service_centers"
               class="- topic/xref "/> immediately.</p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">Always check that the crates are transported correctly according
to the markings on the crates. It is important to examine the crates,
boxes, cases, pallets and other packages for any transportation damage
before, during and after unloading.</p>
      <hazardstatement conref="../Library/Warnings_Library_0000325173.dita#war_lib/never_install_damaged_systems"
                       class="+ topic/note hazard-d/hazardstatement ">
         <messagepanel class="+ topic/ul hazard-d/messagepanel ">
            <typeofhazard class="+ topic/li hazard-d/typeofhazard "/>
            <howtoavoid class="+ topic/li hazard-d/howtoavoid "/>
         </messagepanel>
      </hazardstatement>
      <p class="- topic/p ">If any damage is found, immediately document the extent of the
damage, contact <xref conref="../Library/Reference_Library_CPT_0000338844.dita#Reference_Library-69E2C789/Reality_service_centers"
               class="- topic/xref "/> and file a damage claim to the shipping agency <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">within
24 hours</b>. Always record all findings, especially if:</p>
      <ul class="- topic/ul ">
         <li class="- topic/li ">
            <p class="- topic/p ">Severe damage to the crate is discovered. The crate and equipment
must be left untouched until the shipper and insurance company can
inspect it.</p>
         </li>
         <li class="- topic/li ">
            <p class="- topic/p ">The crate, boxes, cases or other packing are found very wet
or dirty. Always keep the crate, boxes, cases and any packing for
inspection together with its content.</p>
         </li>
         <li class="- topic/li ">
            <p class="- topic/p ">Any hidden damage that could only be noticed after unpacking
needs to be recorded and photographed in detail. Submit a report of
the findings and evidence within 7 days of discovery, or within 3
days of discovery in case of sea freight</p>
         </li>
      </ul>
